title: 131: The Walmart Haul Episode (January '21 Edition)
itunes:title: The Walmart Haul Episode (January '21 Edition)
description: This week, Lisa, Mikey, and Jamie are chewing some really tasty finds from Walmart like a new vegan beef bowl from Healthy Choice, a 60-calorie pita bread, classic cereals turned into snack mixes, and walnut butter that Mikey fell in love with! Plus, an açaí bowl that Lisa gave a 10 out of 10! So turn off the TV, put down that book, and push play right now! Then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of the products mentioned in the episode.
itunes:summary: Stop everything you’re doing... We’re going to Walmart on this week’s episode of Chew the Right Thing!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
